Fountain of Blood.~
You stand in a quiet town square. Everything seems to be normal until
you see the huge demonic fountain before you. Faces of demons grining evilly
and unholy scenes of death cover this magical fountain. Then you notice that
it isn't water the fountain is spurting from its maw...it is Blood! The blood
of the people who are sacrificed here in the square of death. Demonic voices
fill your head..."sacrifice the weak to us...give this ground blood...The
kill rewards" You hear praises of power and the promises new equipment fill 
your mind. You could have power if you were to make a sacrifice here. The 
choice is yours to make.
~
