Alter to Immortals.~
You stand in a large room of gold and concrete pillers. The pillers
rise before you like a giant rises before a child. You are in a state of 
awe at how huge this place is. In the center of the room is a large open 
area. Inside this area is a large gold alter. Swords are floating silently
in the air on opposide sides of the alter. Then you hear a voice... " Brave
soul who has entered this chamber...come forward and hear us." You feel 
yourself being pulled forward and nod. "You stand in a place of high honor
today. Place upon our alter a sacrifice and you shall be rewarded. You
will be able to keep all the possessions of the mortal that you slay. Come
forward and take victory for us. Spill blood and feel power."
~
