#5908
Dragons Den.~
Heat rises from the floor of this immense cavern. You feel sweat 
beading upon your brow and notice a HUGE black dragon sleeping silently
before you. Then as soon as you notice the dragon one of its yellow evil
eyes opens and stares at you. You feel a wave of panic come over you as it
seems to penetrate to your soul. Then the dragon smiles, wicked teeth as 
sharp as anything you can imagine shining in the light. The dragon then
speaks, "Brave adventurer, fear me not. I will not slay you. You will slay
someone though and give me his corpse for I am hungry. I care not who wins,
for all I want is blood."
~
