#5909
Swamp of Lost Souls.~
You stand in a marshy swamp. Bats fly over you like a silent wave
of death. The air is hungry as is the swamp at your feet. The wind blows a
cold breeze that seems to penetrate to your very soul. The howling of wolves
can be heard as well as ancient battle cries. Then you see two ghostly forms
of two armored knights fighting each other...Ah, the glory of battle. They 
turn and regard you with curiousity. Then in unison they speak. "Brave soul 
who has entered the swamp, hear us. Pkilling is something of great honor and
the swamp is a place that tests the skills of the players true abilities. 
Show us how you kill." The breeze picks up momentum and You suddenly hear 
thousends of souls crying for battle. This is your chance to show them that 
you too are worthy of honor.
~
